Project context:
- React 19 + Vite 7 + TypeScript
- Feature-based architecture with dependency flow `shared -> features -> app`

Conventions:
- New user-facing work goes into `src/features/`
- Route definitions stay in `src/app/routes.tsx`
- Shared primitives go into `src/shared/`
- Use `@/` alias imports
- Prefer CSS Modules
- Avoid `any`
- Run `pnpm lint` before finishing
